@startuml engine-store
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class VectorStore {
  - _client : PersistentClient
  - _col : Collection
  --
  + __init__(persist_dir: Path,\n           collection_name: str = "kb_chunks")
  + add(ids: list[str], embeddings: list[list[float]],\n      documents: list[str], metadatas: list[dict]) : void
  + delete(ids: list[str]) : void
  + delete_by_source(source_file: str) : void
  + query(embedding: list[float],\n        n_results: int) : list[dict]
  + count() : int
  + get_ids() : list[str]
}

note right of VectorStore
  Backend: ChromaDB PersistentClient
  Index space: cosine (HNSW)
  Converts distance → similarity:
    score = 1.0 - dist
  add() is upsert-safe — existing IDs
  are updated, not duplicated.
  Empty-collection guard in query()
  and delete_by_source().
  delete_by_source() uses ChromaDB
  where-filter on metadata.source_file
  — no chunk ID tracking required.
end note

@enduml
